对于根据路径变量动态调用不同Service的场景，可以考虑使用 策略模式 结合 工厂模式。以下是详细实现：

方案一：策略模式 + 工厂模式

1. 定义策略接口

```java
// 1. 定义策略接口
public interface IProcessStrategy {
    /**
     * 处理请求
     */
    String process(String request);
    
    /**
     * 支持的策略类型
     */
    String getType();
}

// 2. 创建策略上下文（非必需，用于统一管理）
@Component
public class StrategyContext {
    
    @Autowired
    private final Map<String, IProcessStrategy> strategyMap = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();
    
    // Spring会自动注入所有IProcessStrategy实现
    @Autowired
    public StrategyContext(List<IProcessStrategy> strategies) {
        for (IProcessStrategy strategy : strategies) {
            strategyMap.put(strategy.getType(), strategy);
        }
    }
    
    public IProcessStrategy getStrategy(String type) {
        IProcessStrategy strategy = strategyMap.get(type);
        if (strategy == null) {
            throw new IllegalArgumentException("Unknown strategy type: " + type);
        }
        return strategy;
    }
}
```

2. 实现具体策略

```java
// 3. 具体策略实现
@Service
public class UserProcessStrategy implements IProcessStrategy {
    
    @Override
    public String process(String request) {
        return "Processing user request: " + request;
    }
    
    @Override
    public String getType() {
        return "user";
    }
}

@Service
public class OrderProcessStrategy implements IProcessStrategy {
    
    @Override
    public String process(String request) {
        return "Processing order request: " + request;
    }
    
    @Override
    public String getType() {
        return "order";
    }
}

@Service
public class ProductProcessStrategy implements IProcessStrategy {
    
    @Override
    public String process(String request) {
        return "Processing product request: " + request;
    }
    
    @Override
    public String getType() {
        return "product";
    }
}
```

3. Controller实现

```java
// 4. Controller层
@RestController
@RequestMapping("/api")
public class ProcessController {
    
    @Autowired
    private StrategyContext strategyContext;
    
    /**
     * 根据类型动态调用不同策略
     * @param type 路径变量：user/order/product等
     * @param request 请求参数
     */
    @PostMapping("/process/{type}")
    public ResponseEntity<?> process(
            @PathVariable("type") String type,
            @RequestBody String request) {
        
        IProcessStrategy strategy = strategyContext.getStrategy(type);
        String result = strategy.process(request);
        
        return ResponseEntity.ok(result);
    }
}
```

方案二：使用ServiceLocator模式（更简洁）

1. 创建服务定位器

```java
@Component
public class ServiceLocator {
    
    private final Map<String, IProcessService> serviceMap = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();
    
    @Autowired
    public ServiceLocator(List<IProcessService> services) {
        // 使用注解或约定获取服务标识
        for (IProcessService service : services) {
            if (service instanceof ProcessService) {
                ProcessService processService = (ProcessService) service;
                serviceMap.put(processService.getServiceType(), service);
            }
        }
    }
    
    public IProcessService getService(String serviceType) {
        IProcessService service = serviceMap.get(serviceType);
        if (service == null) {
            throw new ServiceNotFoundException("Service not found for type: " + serviceType);
        }
        return service;
    }
}
```

2. 定义服务接口和实现

```java
// 服务接口
public interface IProcessService {
    String handleRequest(String request);
}

// 基类（可选，用于规范）
public abstract class ProcessService implements IProcessService {
    public abstract String getServiceType();
}

// 具体实现
@Service
public class UserService extends ProcessService {
    
    @Override
    public String handleRequest(String request) {
        return "User Service: " + request;
    }
    
    @Override
    public String getServiceType() {
        return "user";
    }
}

@Service
public class OrderService extends ProcessService {
    
    @Override
    public String handleRequest(String request) {
        return "Order Service: " + request;
    }
    
    @Override
    public String getServiceType() {
        return "order";
    }
}
```

3. 使用枚举管理类型（推荐）

```java
// 5. 使用枚举定义类型（更规范）
public enum ProcessType {
    USER("user", "用户处理"),
    ORDER("order", "订单处理"),
    PRODUCT("product", "产品处理");
    
    private final String code;
    private final String desc;
    
    ProcessType(String code, String desc) {
        this.code = code;
        this.desc = desc;
    }
    
    public String getCode() {
        return code;
    }
    
    public static ProcessType fromCode(String code) {
        for (ProcessType type : values()) {
            if (type.code.equalsIgnoreCase(code)) {
                return type;
            }
        }
        throw new IllegalArgumentException("Unknown process type: " + code);
    }
}

// 策略工厂改进版
@Component
public class ProcessStrategyFactory {
    
    @Autowired
    private Map<String, IProcessStrategy> strategyMap;
    
    public IProcessStrategy getStrategy(ProcessType type) {
        return strategyMap.get(type.getCode());
    }
}
```

4. 改进的Controller

```java
@RestController
@RequestMapping("/api/v2")
public class ImprovedController {
    
    @Autowired
    private ProcessStrategyFactory strategyFactory;
    
    @PostMapping("/process/{type}")
    public ResponseEntity<?> process(
            @PathVariable("type") String typeStr,
            @RequestBody String request) {
        
        // 1. 验证和转换类型
        ProcessType type;
        try {
            type = ProcessType.fromCode(typeStr);
        } catch (IllegalArgumentException e) {
            return ResponseEntity.badRequest()
                    .body("Invalid process type: " + typeStr);
        }
        
        // 2. 获取策略并执行
        IProcessStrategy strategy = strategyFactory.getStrategy(type);
        String result = strategy.process(request);
        
        // 3. 返回结果
        return ResponseEntity.ok(result);
    }
}
```

方案三：使用反射的动态调用（最灵活）

```java
@Component
public class DynamicServiceInvoker {
    
    @Autowired
    private ApplicationContext applicationContext;
    
    /**
     * 根据服务名动态调用
     */
    public Object invokeService(String serviceName, String methodName, Object... args) {
        // 获取Bean名称（可以配置映射关系）
        String beanName = serviceName + "ServiceImpl";
        
        Object service = applicationContext.getBean(beanName);
        
        try {
            // 找到对应方法（可根据参数类型更精确匹配）
            Method method = Arrays.stream(service.getClass().getMethods())
                    .filter(m -> m.getName().equals(methodName))
                    .findFirst()
                    .orElseThrow(() -> new NoSuchMethodException(methodName));
            
            return method.invoke(service, args);
            
        } catch (Exception e) {
            throw new RuntimeException("Service invocation failed", e);
        }
    }
}
```

